com.viaoa.html

Class OABase

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.html.OABase
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    OAApplication, OAForm, OASession, OASystem

    public abstract class OABase
extends Object
implements Serializable
    base class used by OAForm, OASession, OAApplication, OASystem for storing objects and messages. For objects, all Hubs are stored in a seperate hashtable, all other objects are stored in another hashtable.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
